## Development

### Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/lhassa8/skillforge.git
cd skillforge
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### Run Tests

```bash
pytest tests/ -v
pytest tests/ -v --cov=skillforge  # With coverage
```

### Code Quality

```bash
ruff check skillforge/
mypy skillforge/
```

